s=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最緊要有被動 比人追尾一被動又過骨<br />\n打坦克垂直插落去轟勁爽<br />\n連狙自從學識左戰機就好小用<br />\n不過玩戰機有樣野唔好 炸到變惡劣玩家<br />\n依家仲坐緊 要坐兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打玩ps4定pc"},{"pid":"e2020b83d09882ece504587d6630783f58f52646","tid":241674,"uid":12127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Csgo GE 不過 overwatch 得3600 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncsgo ge overwarch 唔過3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eccf719ac533cd9319c5bfb9156ba8a00f7854","tid":241674,"uid":60598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"war3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問打機 槍game冇槍法 LOL冇技術冇運氣<br />\naoc無策略廢控兵<br />\n<br />\n自問最叻仔都係war3啲小遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不可能的boss打到普難 彈彈波略有小成，其他小遊戲地圖都叫中高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de5fb5f48d0d6c2288d94e27387bf69cc43a15e","tid":241674,"uid":35993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>GTA V 掛<br />\n打街場打到成日比鬼仔 台仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連狙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連狙 戰機都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但死鬥個d玩唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排負碌用坦克打撚中架九頭蛇，個鬼仔嬲撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\