普通飛機完全追唔到咁制，打坦克我通常都係用野人，一次過五粒轟落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戰機學極都唔撚識，掃完地會拉唔返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無入連登個PS4 Group呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多勁人，我新手，不了</blockquote><br />\n新舊都係咁玩架喇"},{"pid":"1e961987cc3113ec913e3cc76e99861445653a10","tid":241674,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"舊 bio hazard"},{"pid":"0dc21f05403ebd8d39aa9571d2a526fde9382667","tid":241674,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"CS 1.5 <br />\n中學日日玩~ 特別係中二三~ <br />\n以前好窮無電腦~ 一定要去網吧~<br />\n入到去網吧一定殺爆對手~ <br />\n其實勁唔勁都係其次~ D人尊敬你先係皇道~ <br />\n因為全部人都係玩CS~ <br />\n所以就算你係死靚仔~ 只要玩得勁<br />\nD人都會撩你講野~ 因為想同你一隊~"},{"pid":"ab210d8135e233e1a997cbe40062a9561cd33e8f","tid":241674,"uid":65545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fb3f68fdc9f7b06114f71a8c7a8c4ee68321b1f","tid":241674,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"123紅綠燈過馬路要小心"},{"pid":"b6af853e0feaa0ef9b41ac05c0102bc2cb1ce123","tid":241674,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>123紅綠燈過馬路要小心</blockquote><br />\n樓下公園連續三年霸主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3a45db937354469ebf96f6b80fb6bc6d4fc978","tid":241674,"uid":7769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"忍豆風雲 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7c0baa26bd758a792c8d7170989c9accaefaf7","tid":241674,"uid":35758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl